# Applications Folder

This folder stores your job application outputs organized by company.

Structure:
```
applications/
├── company-name/
│   ├── resume.md
│   ├── resume.pdf
│   ├── cover-letter.md
│   ├── cover-letter.pdf
│   └── notes.md
```

## Converting to PDF

Option 1: Use pandoc (recommended)
```bash
brew install pandoc
pandoc resume.md -o resume.pdf
```

Option 2: Use a Markdown editor (Typora, iA Writer, etc.)
- Open .md file → Export as PDF

Option 3: Use VS Code
- Install "Markdown PDF" extension
- Right-click .md file → Markdown PDF: Export (pdf)

Option 4: Online converter
- Copy markdown to https://markdowntohtml.com
- Print to PDF from browser
